  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400\u202f\u00b0F (200\u202f\u00b0C).",
    "Wrap beets in foil and bake for 45\u201360\u202fmin until tender; cool and peel.",
    "Place eggs in boiling water for 9\u202fmin, then transfer to ice water, peel, and dice.",
    "Roast fennel slices in the oven for 10\u202fmin, or saut\u00e9 until lightly browned.",
    "Whisk apple cider vinegar, olive oil, Dijon mustard, honey, salt, and pepper in a bowl to make the dressing.",
    "Combine beets, pickled greens, eggs, walnuts, and roasted fennel in a large bowl.",
    "Pour dressing over the salad and toss gently to coat evenly.",
    "Serve immediately or chill for 15\u202fmin for flavors to meld."
  ],
